  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is lightly browned.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the curry powder, cumin, and cayenne pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the coconut milk, tomato paste, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 1 1/2 hours.",
    "Use a whisk to stir the curry occasionally as it simmers.",
    "Serve the curry hot, garnished with fresh cilantro if desired."
